{
  "texts": [
    "A.1 Algorithms",
    "In our paper, we introduce the first version of our method, JUMP*, an algorithm that optimizes adversarial multi-prompts, focusing on attacking LLMs to generate jailbroken responses on a set of malicious data.",
    "The details of JUMP* are shown in Algorithm 1.",
    "To address the issue of readability, we propose the final version, JUMP, which integrates perplexity control into JUMP*.",
    "The details of the Constraints step are shown in Algorithm 2."
  ]
}